            code: `Modus Ponens:
  Premise 1: P → Q
  Premise 2: P
  ─────────────
  Conclusion: Q

Modus Tollens:
  Premise 1: P → Q
  Premise 2: ¬Q
  ─────────────
  Conclusion: ¬P

And-Elimination:
  Premise: P ∧ Q
  ─────────────
  Conclusion: P   (or Q)

Or-Introduction:
  Premise: P
  ─────────────
  Conclusion: P ∨ Q

Resolution:
  Premise 1: P ∨ Q
  Premise 2: ¬P ∨ R
  ─────────────
  Conclusion: Q ∨ R`,
