            code: `Quantifier Negation:
  ¬∀x P(x)  ≡  ∃x ¬P(x)
  ¬∃x P(x)  ≡  ∀x ¬P(x)

Quantifier Distribution:
  ∀x (P(x) ∧ Q(x))  ≡  ∀x P(x) ∧ ∀x Q(x)
  ∃x (P(x) ∨ Q(x))  ≡  ∃x P(x) ∨ ∃x Q(x)

Conversion to Prenex Normal Form:
  ∀x P(x) → ∃y Q(y)
  ≡ ¬∀x P(x) ∨ ∃y Q(y)
  ≡ ∃x ¬P(x) ∨ ∃y Q(y)
  ≡ ∃x ∃y (¬P(x) ∨ Q(y))

Skolemization (eliminate ∃):
  ∀x ∃y Loves(y, x)
  → ∀x Loves(Skolem(x), x)
  
  Where Skolem(x) is a new function symbol`,
