            title: 'Example: Harris Corner Response',
            code: `1. Compute image gradients:
   Ix = ∂I/∂x,  Iy = ∂I/∂y

2. Form structure tensor M at each pixel:
   M = [ Σ(Ix²)   Σ(Ix·Iy) ]
       [ Σ(Ix·Iy) Σ(Iy²)   ]
   (sums over a local window)

3. Compute corner response:
   R = det(M) - k · trace(M)²
     = λ₁λ₂ - k(λ₁ + λ₂)²

4. Threshold R:
   R > threshold → corner detected

Interpretation:
   λ₁ ≈ 0, λ₂ ≈ 0: flat region
   λ₁ >> 0, λ₂ ≈ 0: edge
   λ₁ >> 0, λ₂ >> 0: corner`,
