          code: `EDA workflow & what each plot reveals

Line plot        -> trend? seasonality? outliers?
Seasonal plot    -> stable or evolving seasonality?
  2019  /\\/__    2020  /\\/__    (compare years)
ACF / PACF       -> AR vs MA order
  ACF  tails off    PACF cuts at p  => AR(p)
  ACF  cuts at q    PACF tails off  => MA(q)
Rolling mean/var -> non-stationarity (drift, vol clusters)
Histogram        -> normality? heavy tails? outliers?`,
