          heading: 'Visual Representation',
          code: `ADF decision logic

  Run ADF on Y:
    p-value > 0.05  ->  fail to reject H0  ->  has unit root (non-stat.)
    p-value < 0.05  ->  reject H0          ->  stationary

  If non-stationary:
    Y -> diff(Y) -> run ADF again
    repeat until p < 0.05; count differences = d

  Confirm with KPSS (null = stationary):
    ADF rejects + KPSS fails to reject  =>  strong: stationary
    ADF fails   + KPSS rejects          =>  strong: non-stationary`,
